dimensions: Overall: 180.3 x 193.4 cm (5 ft. 11 in. x 6 ft. 4 1/8 in.)
title: Les Jardins Francais
description: Three panel screen, featuring classically-styled building in center, with colonnade running to left side of panel, containing nine figural sculptures. In front of building is obelisk. In foreground are two seated figures, with woman holding small child, in front of monument topped with beast. The back of each screen is divided into three sections by crossbars, each containing a printed green square on dark gray ground.
name: Screen panels
